t: "Monhw־µ nso na moannkum onipa a Nyankopֽ»n abra (ne kum, anaa Way־µ no kronkron), gyes־µ ־µnam ne kwan so. Obia y־µbeku no ֽ»kwan bֽ»ne soֽ» no, nokor־µ s־µ Yג€™ama ne kyitaafoֽ» no tumi (s־µ ֽ»hwehw־µ at־µn teneee, anaas־µ ֽ»gye mogya ho sika anaas־µ ֽ»de ky־µ); nanso ֽ»nhw־µ na wany־µ bֽ»ne wֽ» okum no ho, efiris־µ, (aban) b־µboa no"